INSERT INTO `quotes` VALUES (1,'Your mental health is a priority. Your happiness is essential. Your self-care is a necessity.','Unknown','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(2,'Recovery is not one and done. It is a lifelong journey that takes place one day, one step at a time.','Unknown','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(3,'You don\'t have to control your thoughts. You just have to stop letting them control you.','Dan Millman','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(4,'Self-care is not selfish. You cannot serve from an empty vessel.','Eleanor Brown','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(5,'Mental health problems don\'t define who you are. They are something you experience.','Roy Chue','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(6,'The strongest people are those who win battles we know nothing about.','Unknown','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(7,'You are not alone. You are seen. You are heard. You are loved.','Unknown','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(8,'Your present circumstances don\'t determine where you can go; they merely determine where you start.','Nido Qubein','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(9,'Sometimes the bad things that happen in our lives put us directly on the path to the best things that will ever happen to us.','Nicole Reed','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(10,'You don\'t have to be positive all the time. It\'s perfectly okay to feel sad, angry, annoyed, frustrated, scared and anxious.','Lori Deschene','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(11,'Take a deep breath. It\'s just a bad day, not a bad life.','Unknown','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(12,'You are stronger than you know, braver than you believe, and smarter than you think.','A.A. Milne','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(13,'The only journey is the one within.','Rainer Maria Rilke','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(14,'Mental health is not a destination, but a process.','Noam Shpancer','mental health','2024-11-26 04:16:12'),(15,'Be gentle